+## WebSocket Relay (Cloud Run)
+
+### Dockerfile
+
+```dockerfile
+FROM node:20-slim
+
+WORKDIR /app
+
+COPY package*.json ./
+RUN npm ci --only=production
+
+COPY . .
+
+EXPOSE 8080
+
